data.description: Showings start Friday 4/26. Welcome to this charming split-level home! This delightful residence boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths, each featuring a convenient tub-shower combo for your comfort and convenience. As you step inside, you are greeted with tile flooring and vaulted ceilings in the living room. The well-appointed kitchen comes equipped with a handy pantry, ensuring you have ample storage space for all your culinary needs. The basement boasts a rec room and cozy fireplace. Outside, you'll find a fenced-in yard offering privacy, along with a shed for additional storage. Enjoy outdoor gatherings or simply unwind on the inviting deck, overlooking the corner lot. Located close to parks and Offutt AFB! Don't miss out on this wonderful opportunity to make this house your forever home!
